{
    "name": "test channel 123",
    "source": "whatsapp",
    "sender": "Alice",
    "receiver": "Bob",
    "receiverPronoun": "Him",
    "messageSource": [
        {
            "body": "Hey, how was your day?",
            "sender": "Alice",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T08:00:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "It was good, thanks for asking! How about yours?",
            "sender": "Bob",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T08:05:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "Mine was a bit hectic, had lots of meetings.",
            "sender": "Alice",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T08:10:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "That sounds exhausting. Did you get some time to relax?",
            "sender": "Bob",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T08:15:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "Yeah, I did some yoga in the evening. It helped a lot.",
            "sender": "Alice",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T08:20:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "Yoga sounds nice. I should try it sometime.",
            "sender": "Bob",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T08:25:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "You definitely should! It’s very relaxing.",
            "sender": "Alice",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T08:30:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "What poses do you recommend for beginners?",
            "sender": "Bob",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T08:35:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "Start with some basic poses like Child's Pose and Downward Dog.",
            "sender": "Alice",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T08:40:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "Thanks for the tips! By the way, did you get a chance to look at the project proposal?",
            "sender": "Bob",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T08:45:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "Yes, I did. I think it looks great, but we might need to adjust the budget a bit.",
            "sender": "Alice",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T08:50:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "I was thinking the same. We can discuss it more in the meeting tomorrow.",
            "sender": "Bob",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T08:55:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "Sure, let’s finalize it then.",
            "sender": "Alice",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T09:00:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "Perfect. Are you free tonight? Maybe we can grab dinner.",
            "sender": "Bob",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T09:05:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "I’d love to! Where should we go?",
            "sender": "Alice",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T09:10:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "How about that new Italian place downtown?",
            "sender": "Bob",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T09:15:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "Sounds good! I’ll see you at 7?",
            "sender": "Alice",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T09:20:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "7 it is. Looking forward to it!",
            "sender": "Bob",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T09:25:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "Hey, are you on your way?",
            "sender": "Alice",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T18:45:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "Yes, just left the house. See you in 15 minutes!",
            "sender": "Bob",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T18:50:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "Great, I’m almost there too.",
            "sender": "Alice",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T18:55:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "I got us a table near the window. Perfect view!",
            "sender": "Bob",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T19:10:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "Nice choice! This place looks amazing.",
            "sender": "Alice",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T19:15:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "What do you feel like having?",
            "sender": "Bob",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T19:20:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "I’m thinking of trying the pasta. What about you?",
            "sender": "Alice",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T19:25:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "Pasta sounds good. I might go with the lasagna.",
            "sender": "Bob",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T19:30:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "Lasagna is always a good choice.",
            "sender": "Alice",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T19:35:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "By the way, how’s your family doing?",
            "sender": "Bob",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T19:40:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "They’re doing well, thanks for asking! How about yours?",
            "sender": "Alice",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T19:45:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "Everyone is good. My sister just got a new job.",
            "sender": "Bob",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T19:50:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "Oh, that’s great news! What is she doing now?",
            "sender": "Alice",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T19:55:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "She’s working as a graphic designer at a startup.",
            "sender": "Bob",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T20:00:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "That sounds like a cool job! I’m sure she’ll do great.",
            "sender": "Alice",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T20:05:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "I think so too. She’s really excited about it.",
            "sender": "Bob",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T20:10:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "What did you think of the food?",
            "sender": "Alice",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T20:30:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "It was delicious! We should come here again.",
            "sender": "Bob",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T20:35:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "Absolutely! I had a great time tonight.",
            "sender": "Alice",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T20:40:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "Me too. Let’s do this more often.",
            "sender": "Bob",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T20:45:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "Definitely. Have a good night!",
            "sender": "Alice",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T21:00:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "Good night, Alice!",
            "sender": "Bob",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-28T21:05:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "Good morning! Did you sleep well?",
            "sender": "Alice",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-29T08:00:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "Morning! Yes, I did. How about you?",
            "sender": "Bob",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-29T08:05:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "I slept like a baby. Feeling refreshed!",
            "sender": "Alice",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-29T08:10:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "That’s good to hear. What’s your plan for today?",
            "sender": "Bob",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-29T08:15:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "I’m going to a yoga class in the morning, then probably just relax at home.",
            "sender": "Alice",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-29T08:20:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "Sounds like a relaxing day. Enjoy your yoga class!",
            "sender": "Bob",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-29T08:25:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "Thanks! What about you? Any plans?",
            "sender": "Alice",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-29T08:30:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "I’m meeting some friends for brunch, then maybe a movie in the afternoon.",
            "sender": "Bob",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-29T08:35:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "Sounds fun! Enjoy your day!",
            "sender": "Alice",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-29T08:40:00"
        },
        {
            "body": "You too, Alice!",
            "sender": "Bob",
            "sentAt": "2024-06-29T08:45:00"
        }
    ]
}
